Package semsim.model.computational.units

Class UnitFactor

java.lang.Object
semsim.model.computational.units.UnitFactor
public class UnitFactor
extends java.lang.Object
When specifying the physical units for a model variable, unit factors are used to indicate the more fundamental units that make up a physical unit.
Author:
mneal
